<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天<delay20 />我做了一個夢，<delay20 />
我夢見我轉開水龍頭，
結果竟然跑出了<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是喔～？<20_2 arg="4" /><delay frames="40" />
如果是預知夢，那就太厲害了呢～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="3" />然後我前天<delay20 />則是做了一個
從水龍頭裡
跑出醬油的夢<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不是<delay8 />累了啊<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="4" />醬油可以淋在很多食物上吃，
這樣很好啊！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />不過如果是從水龍頭出來，<delay20 />
流出一丁點就要馬上關掉，<delay8 />
不然可不妙呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
我總覺得你正面的想法<delay8 />
救贖了我呢。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那今天……<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想做個從水龍頭
跑出鮮奶油的夢！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後我前天<delay20 />則是做了一個
從水龍頭裡跑出義大利麵的夢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不是<delay8 />累了啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那不是超棒的嗎！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />既然飲料和義大利麵
都跑出來了，<delay8 />那今天<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />該不會<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />輪到甜點了吧！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
我總覺得你正面的想法<delay8 />
救贖了我呢。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那今天……<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想做個從水龍頭
跑出洋菜涼粉的夢！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後我前天<delay20 />則是做了一個
從水龍頭裡跑出牙膏的夢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不是<delay8 />累了啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯？<20_2 arg="4" /><delay frames="40" />
牙膏冒出來之後，<delay8 />
隔天才冒出了飲料？<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那順序不就顛倒了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該是先喝飲料再刷牙吧！？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
這點<delay8 />真的應該生氣吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
能聽到你這麼說，<delay8 />
我覺得自己被救贖了！
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣我開始期待今天夢裡……<delay8 />
會跑出什麼東西來了呢，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你將來的夢想<delay8 />是什麼呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那還用說嗎？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然是，要當上國民偶像啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是那種一打開電視，
就隨時會出現的<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />偶像！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="5" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
要是你成了國民偶像，<delay8 />
我當然替你感到開心<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是這樣的話，<delay8 />像我這種普通人
就沒辦法找你講話了呢！<delay frames="40" />
這樣我會很寂寞的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那也沒辦法呢，<delay frames="40" />
畢竟是偶像嘛！<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />真是的～<delay20 />
別露出那種表情嘛！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會給你簽名的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
如果不是那麼厲害的偶像，<delay8 />
而是島民偶像的話，你覺得可以嗎？<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過就算是這樣，<delay8 />
我還是會不太敢找你講話<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂喂，<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我早就已經是島民偶像了，<delay20 />
你沒注意到嗎？
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算我是島民偶像，<delay8 />
你還是超常來找我講話的耶～！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來今年<tag a="110" b="17" /><delay8 />
是流行這種風格的啊。<delay frames="40" />
真是讓我學到許多呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="4" />我還知道接下來<delay20 />
可能會流行什麼喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說～<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
你那口頭禪<delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還滿不錯的耶！<delay frames="40" />
也可以讓我用嗎？</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！<delay20 />真的嗎？<delay frames="40" />
當然，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你一定要用用看喔！</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你～！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻，<delay20 />感覺還不賴呢！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
我的口頭禪被你一用，<delay8 />
感覺也會流行起來呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>